title: Adventureland.Greg.Mottola.2008.Script
description:
This is a new movie set to star Ryan Reynolds and Kristen Stewart.  It is slated for an August release in the USA.  Check out the screenplay now.

A comedy set in the summer of 1987 and centered around a recent college grad (Eisenberg) who takes a nowhere job at his local amusement park, only to find it&#039;s the perfect course to get him prepared for the real world.
